seeing and navigate them throughout the property.\n\nOff-the-plan properties have been sold in the same way for years with brochures, high-quality photo renders, and stylish display suites. Whilst they do the trick, here at EnvisionVR we like to take things to the next level. That's why we created our world-first EnvisionVR app which allows you to view your future project in high-fidelity Virtual Reality and Augmented Reality using a VR headset or smart device. Our VR experiences are completely mobile, multi-person and collaborative coupled with an easy- to-use interface that will enhance your sales process.", "short_description": "Our EnvisionVR app allows you to view your future projects in high-fidelity Virtual Reality.\n\nCreate virtual inspections of your off-the-plan properties in VR. You can talk to buyers in real-time, explain what they are seeing and navigate them throughout the property."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://envisionvr.net/app-privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://envisionvr.net/app-terms-of-use/", "publisher_name": "Envision VR Pty Ltd", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://envisionvr.net/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["UTILITY"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["HAND_TRACKING", "OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER"], "id": "472978657736445"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "424431802146958"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "424431802146958"}, "is_approved": 